high_descs: Move to the right side of the sink to the left of the kitchen table
Pick up the spatula from the counter top
Move to the table behind and to the right of you
Place spatula inside pot on the left side table
Pick up pot from the table
Move to the right side of the sink to the left of you
Place pot onto the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spatula in it next to the sink.

high_descs: Move to the counter right of the sink.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Bring the spatula to the table.
Put the spatula in the pan on the table.
Pick up the pan with spatula in it.
Bring the pan to the counter right of sink.
Put the pan on the counter right of sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with spatula on the counter to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spatula that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk until there is a white table to your left then turn to face it and walk to it.
Put the spatula in the square frying pan.
Pick up the frying pan with the spatula in it.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Put the pan on the counter directly below the orange bag.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan that has a spatula in it on the counter.
